## Technical & Narrative Recommendations

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Narrative Consistency Fix**: You MUST decide if the creature escapes s21 or if they take it out s22. The "manual return" (s22) allows for a more planned, heroic climax, whereas the "escape" (s21) creates a more frantic search.

> [!TIP]
> **Terminology Audit**: Unify the descriptions of the "Red-Eyes." Stick to a consistent name (e.g., "The Cancelers" or "The Void-Beings") once their nature is understood by the characters.

> [!WARNING]
> **Dialogue Refinement**: Makayla's voice oscillates between "teenager" and "university professor." Lean into her being a "brilliant but isolated" polymath to make her technical prowess feel earned.
